caption: This spot constantly delivers. They have fresh food for reasonable pricing, there no long wait even when the place is full.

The staff were very attentive and friendly which was a plus.  The addition of a private parking lot in the back for a restaurant on Sunset was huge too.  I am very curious to come back and try other dishes because I feel the ones I chose were not of my particular preference.
